title: Running rustc -V  binary on SailfishOS 2.0.1.11 (Taalojärvi) (armv7hl) raised Exception

labels.name: O-Arm
labels.description: Target: 32-bit Arm processors (armv6, armv7, thumb...), including 64-bit Arm in AArch32 state

body:
